data.description: This VA qualifying assumption is at a remarkable 2.5% rate! This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath gem is nestled in a truly unique area, combining the tranquility of an urban oasis with the convenience of being close to shopping, restaurants and the interstate. You’ll have everything at your doorstep saving you time and stress. This home has two living areas, a secluded master bedroom with master bath fully loaded with double sinks, a tub and separate shower. The den has a cozy fireplace. The slab was built with a Post Tension Cable System. The attic is complete with a solar attic fan and pest control insulation. A BONUS half bath is located in the garage.  Perfect for growing families or anyone looking for a comfortable stylish place to call home. Don’t let this opportunity slip away.
